1) Create Shared Maildir
/var/indimail/bin/maildirmake -S /usr1/shared

2) Create Folder
/var/indimail/bin/maildirmake -s write -f Qmail /usr1/shared/
/var/indimail/bin/maildirmake -s write -f Test /usr1/shared

3) Create Entry in /var/sifmail/etc/maildirshared
qmail	/usr1/shared

Personal Shared Folders

/var/indimail/bin/maildirmake --add shared=/usr1/shared /usr1/manny/Maildir
